F001  
Severity: HIGH  
Category: code-bug  
Type: defect_fix  
Before-behavior: `POST /api/v1/card/parse-answers` 返回 `skeleton`、`layout`、`has_tpl_slots`，前端据此继续预览/生成。  
After-behavior: 本次实现改为只返回 `v2_layout`，删除了 `skeleton`、`layout`、`has_tpl_slots`，但前端仍按旧字段读取。  
Evidence: [src/edu_cloud/modules/card/router.py:553](/C:/Users/Administrator/edu-cloud/src/edu_cloud/modules/card/router.py#L553) [src/edu_cloud/modules/card/router.py:556](/C:/Users/Administrator/edu-cloud/src/edu_cloud/modules/card/router.py#L556)；[frontend/src/pages/ExamDetailPage.vue:750](/C:/Users/Administrator/edu-cloud/frontend/src/pages/ExamDetailPage.vue#L750) [frontend/src/pages/ExamDetailPage.vue:751](/C:/Users/Administrator/edu-cloud/frontend/src/pages/ExamDetailPage.vue#L751) [frontend/src/pages/ExamDetailPage.vue:759](/C:/Users/Administrator/edu-cloud/frontend/src/pages/ExamDetailPage.vue#L759) [frontend/src/pages/ExamDetailPage.vue:902](/C:/Users/Administrator/edu-cloud/frontend/src/pages/ExamDetailPage.vue#L902) [frontend/src/pages/ExamDetailPage.vue:921](/C:/Users/Administrator/edu-cloud/frontend/src/pages/ExamDetailPage.vue#L921)。  
Impact: 上传答案后，前端会把 `parsedSkeleton/parsedLayout/hasTplSlots` 置为 `undefined`/`false`，后续预览和生成路径会退化或直接失效。这是未申报的 API 行为变更，不是 publish 修复的附带安全重构。  
Repair hypothesis: 要么恢复旧响应契约并新增 `v2_layout`，要么同步修改前端消费逻辑并补入口级回归测试。

F002  
Severity: HIGH  
Category: code-bug  
Type: defect_fix  
